        </header>
        <p class="sec-para-main">Usually every webpage only consists of one h1 tag. Heading tags(h1-h6) are put
            on webpage in order i.e. don't use h3 before you have used h2. Heading tags are used for organizing the
            webpage rather than just styling the text.</p>
